---
//@ts-nocheck
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";

const description =
  "Learn about AMOr's mission to support local restaurants and strengthen communities. Discover why shopping local matters and how we're creating a movement for authentic food experiences.";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
const title = "AMOr";
---

<Layout title="AMOr - About" description={description}>
  <main>
    <div class="center">
      <h2>ABOUT US</h2>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
        “The people who give you their food give you their heart” - Ceasar
        Chavez
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="image_container">
      <img src="/images/about_us.webp" alt="hello" class="big_img" />
    </div>
    <Section
      title="THE BEGINNING"
      image="/images/beginning.webp"
      hasButton={false}
      >AMOr began with a simple idea: local businesses deserves more love. Small
      eateries spots are the soul of our cities, and we’re here to help people
      find them, support them, and keep their stories alive. <br /><br />In
      todays world it is getting harder for smaller businesses to withstand
      competition against global corporations. We had to find the solution to
      help the ones that deserve more recognition and love.
      <br /><br />
      People tend to go to city center instead of exploring their own communities
      and areas nearby. This results in money leaving the local economy. That is
      why we found a solution to end this inequality!
    </Section>
    <Section
      title="MISSION AND VISION"
      image="/images/vision.webp"
      hasButton={false}
      background="var(--bun-2)"
      order="-1"
      >Our mission is to bring people closer to the heart of their community by
      inspiring them to discover and support local food businesses. Through
      curiosity, exploration, and shared experiences, we want to make it simple
      and exciting to choose local first.
      <br /><br />Our vision is a future where communities thrive through
      meaningful connections, where neighborhoods are filled with unique tastes,
      stories, and small businesses that stand strong — not overshadowed by
      global competition.
    </Section>
    <Section
      title="STRONGER LOCAL ECONOMIES"
      image="/images/local.webp"
      hasButton={false}
      >Supporting local food businesses isn’t only about great taste, it’s a
      direct investment into the local economy. When people choose independent
      restaurants, cafés, bakeries, and food producers, money stays within the
      community. It circulates between owners, suppliers, workers, and
      residents, leading to more jobs, stronger families, and healthier
      neighborhoods.
    </Section>
    <section class="faq">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 style="padding-top: 0; margin-top: 0;">FAQ</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          Find out more about supporting local economy
        </p>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span
              >Keeps money within the community, helping local families and
              business owners instead of large corporations.</span
            >
            <svg
              class="accordion-icon"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              When you support local businesses, your money circulates within
              the community. This creates a multiplier effect where each dollar
              spent locally generates additional economic activity, supporting
              local jobs, schools, and community services rather than flowing to
              distant corporate headquarters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span
              >Creates local jobs and opportunities for young people and small
              entrepreneurs.</span
            >
            <svg
              class="accordion-icon"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Local businesses are often the first employers for young people
              entering the workforce. They provide training, mentorship, and
              opportunities for entrepreneurship that help build a skilled local
              workforce and inspire the next generation of business owners.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span
              >Builds stronger connections between customers, owners, and the
              community.</span
            >
            <svg
              class="accordion-icon"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Local businesses are run by your neighbors who live in and care
              about your community. They know your name, remember your
              preferences, and invest in local causes. This creates a sense of
              belonging and community cohesion that chain stores simply cannot
              replicate.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span
              >Helps small businesses survive and innovate, increasing choice
              and diversity.</span
            >
            <svg
              class="accordion-icon"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Small businesses bring unique products, services, and experiences
              to your community. Your support enables them to experiment with
              new ideas, maintain quality standards, and offer alternatives to
              mass-market options, creating a more diverse and interesting local
              landscape.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-header">
            <span
              >Promotes sustainable growth, as money circulates locally multiple
              times rather than leaving the area.</span
            >
            <svg
              class="accordion-icon"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              Studies show that for every $100 spent at a local business,
              approximately $68 stays in the local economy compared to only $43
              when spent at chain stores. This multiplier effect creates
              sustained economic growth and resilience within the community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="center">
        <h2>HOW ME MAKE IT HAPPEN</h2>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          We use interactive digital tools and game-like exploration to
          encourage people to step outside, try new places, and connect with
          local businesses in a fun and meaningful way.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="happen">
        <div class="happen_card">
          <img src="/images/game_index.webp" alt="" />
          <h5>Interactive App</h5>
          <p>An interactive way to virtually explore new eateries</p>
          <Button color="var(--bun-6)" href="/experience">Download Game</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="happen_card">
          <img src="/images/map_index.webp" alt="" />
          <h5>Catalog and Map</h5>
          <p>Catalog with local businesses. Check your area using map.</p>
          <Button color="var(--bun-6)" href="/catalog">Open Catalog</Button>
        </div>
        <div class="happen_card">
          <img src="/images/contact_index.webp" alt="" />
          <h5>Business Profile</h5>
          <p>
            Each local eatery can write their own story and become a part of
            AMOr
          </p>
          <Button color="var(--bun-6)" href="/contact">Sign-up business</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-header").forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const accordionItem = button.parentElement;
        const isOpen = accordionItem?.classList.contains("active");

        // Close all accordion items
        document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-item").forEach((item) => {
          item.classList.remove("active");
        });

        // Open clicked item if it was closed
        if (!isOpen) {
          accordionItem?.classList.add("active");
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .image_container {
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .big_img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 500px;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .faq {
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq h2 {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .accordion-item {
    border: 2px solid var(--cheese-6);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-header {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: "Commissioner", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--cheese-6);
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-header:hover {
    background-color: var(--bun-2);
  }

  .accordion-header span {
    flex: 1;
    padding-right: 1rem;
  }

  .accordion-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    color: var(--cheese-6);
  }

  .accordion-item.active .accordion-icon {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .accordion-content {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .accordion-item.active .accordion-content {
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .accordion-content p {
    padding: 0 1rem 1rem 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--cheese-5);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .center {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
    place-self: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .happen_card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .happen_card {
    width: 300px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .happen {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 8rem;
  }

  .happen p {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .image_container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .big_img {
      max-height: 300px;
    }

    .faq-container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .happen {
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .happen_card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 350px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .image_container {
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .big_img {
      max-height: 200px;
    }

    .faq-container {
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .accordion-header {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.75rem;
    }

    .accordion-content p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0.75rem;
    }

    .happen_card {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .happen_card img {
      height: 150px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    h5 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
